### Microservices Architecture (Battle-Tested)
```yaml
Services:
  auth-service:
    pattern: Stateless JWT
    database: PostgreSQL
    cache: Redis
    monitoring: Prometheus

  business-service:
    pattern: Domain-driven
    database: PostgreSQL
    queue: RabbitMQ
    monitoring: Prometheus

  gateway:
    pattern: API Gateway
    rate-limit: Redis
    cache: Redis
    monitoring: Prometheus

Integration:
  - Service mesh (optional)
  - Event-driven communication
  - Circuit breakers
  - Health checks

Proven: NQH-Bot recovery architecture
```

### Monolithic Architecture (When Appropriate)
```yaml
Structure:
  /apps:
    - Clear module boundaries
    - Shared core services
    - Tenant isolation
    - Performance optimization

Database:
  - Single PostgreSQL
  - Optimized indexes
  - Connection pooling
  - Read replicas

Caching:
  - Redis for sessions
  - Application cache
  - CDN for static

Proven: BFlow Phase 1
Benefits: Simpler deployment, faster development
```

